text: Reinado Internacional del Café 2017 (International Coffee Queen) beauty pageant, was held in Manizales, Colombia, on January 7, 2017. At the end of the event, the outgoing queen Maydeliana Díaz, Reina Internacional del Café 2016 from Venezuela crowned Marilú Acevedo from Mexico as her successor. == Results == {| border="2" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 0 1em 0 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 95%;" |- bgcolor="#efefef" " !
